Primary Location:  United States (US) - Illinois - Moline 
 Function:  Product Engineering 
 Title:  Senior Staff Battery Management System Engineer - 72870 
This position may be located in Moline, IL, Cary, NC, Fargo, ND or Remote per the hiring manager's discretion. This may be dependent on the successful candidate's background, experience, and proficiency. 
This position is currently eligible for a telework and/or a compressed workweek arrangement. The arrangement may be delayed for training or other job acclimation purposes. This arrangement is subject to change. 
Your Responsibilities 
As a  Senior Staff Battery Management System Engineer  you will support product electrification projects by leading and executing the development of lithium-ion battery management systems (BMS) for John Deere products worldwide. This includes product analysis, design, testing, as well as development of advanced battery models and controls. 
Development and commercialization of battery management systems for energy storage (Lithium-Ion batteries) across all John Deere production systems 
Technical leadership for advanced battery management algorithms 
Technical leadership for development of battery models including; electrical, thermal, and aging models 
Technical leadership for identification of appropriate battery technical solutions 
Technical work direction to engineers and lab technicians executing the detailed battery design and testing 
