Understanding of energy storage (Lithium-Ion Battery) technology trends, vehicle industry application trends, battery management system technology trends, and lithium-ion battery test approaches. 
Experience in leading complex engineering projects. 
Work experience with rectifiers, inverters, power control systems, and chargers. 
